# Voice reference audio files for voice cloning
# 
# Place WAV files here for use with Chatterbox voice cloning.
# These files are mounted into the TTS Docker container at /app/voices/
#
# Example usage in TTS request:
#   {
#     "text": "Hello world",
#     "voice_reference": "/app/voices/my-voice.wav"
#   }
#
# Requirements:
#   - WAV format
#   - 5-30 seconds of clean speech
#   - Single speaker
#   - Minimal background noise

